# ── Source / scratch art (not referenced by the live site) ───────────
# Brand source files & generated image scratch live only on local disk.
# The deployed site references ./assets/** exclusively. Keeping these out
# of the production deploy branch avoids shipping ~42MB of unused public
# files. If off-machine backup is wanted, archive them separately.
Logo/
Website Image/
